:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試下換過個枕頭</blockquote><br />\n有無介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用緊Co__ex記憶綿枕頭<br />\n都用咗成年幾 冇再痛<br />\n<br />\nCo__ex：如果可以開名 我先開名"},{"pid":"75b9f69371a3ba58ff6d2554ca01c655d0c5960d","tid":314883,"uid":35240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T16:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搽左安美露又貼埋藥膏布都無用 仲痛緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貼休足得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n休足唔係貼腳架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我揾唔到啲藥膏嗰啲</blockquote><br />\n咁貼左有無用啊？"},{"pid":"04a9ba646e1bfd3d683763efb5591c8888dba577","tid":314883,"uid":118884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T16:48:47.000Z","msg":"濕重 試下飲多d暖水<br />\n做運動出下汗<br />\n唔好飲同食凍野<br />\n調理下身體會好D<br />\n膊頭痛就比錢出去比人按下<br />\n按完包你一覺訓天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3a51922d3bb04e9c9266f6c85a1ca372cdfe03","tid":314883,"uid":35240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試下換過個枕頭</blockquote><br />\n有無介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用緊Co__ex記憶綿枕頭<br />\n都用咗成年幾 冇再痛<br />\n<br />\nCo__ex：如果可以開名 我先開名</blockquote><br />\nGoogle左應該知係邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日買黎試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc487339506d07b9c1a3afba5a7e8d5d27eb5be","tid":314883,"uid":35240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T16:54:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>濕重 試下飲多d暖水<br />\n做運動出下汗<br />\n唔好飲同食凍野<br />\n調理下身體會好D<br />\n膊頭痛就比錢出去比人按下<br />\n按完包你一覺訓天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我已經痛到係街行一陣都開始痛<br />\n平時舉手都唔係點舉到<br />\n我懷疑緊自己係咪有五十肩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">但明明仲後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"723b168f110ec0a186db49b2e9b213504f825c9c","tid":314883,"uid":71154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>濕重 試下飲多d暖水<br />\n做運動出下汗<br />\n唔好飲同食凍野<br />\n調理下身體會好D<br />\n膊頭痛就比錢出去比人按下<br />\n按完包你一覺訓天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實琴日返工已經膊頭酸痛<br />\n佢用啲唔知咩拍我膊頭<br />\n話會好啲<br />\n依加瘀左一大達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要著啲好高領嘅衫<br />\n好肉酸呀"},{"pid":"4b99dfd51c2234338f5f9366cda4a75b73c4355f","tid":314883,"uid":71154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>濕重 試下飲多d暖水<br />\n做運動出下汗<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好飲同食凍野</span><br />\n調理下身體會好D<br />\n膊頭痛就比錢出去比人按下<br />\n按完包你一覺訓天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實琴日返工已經膊頭酸痛<br />\n佢用啲唔知咩拍我膊頭<br />\n話會好啲<br />\n依加瘀左一大達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要著啲好高領嘅衫<br />\n好肉酸呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食左好多凍野最近"},{"pid":"006bd92aa5f1cead6c873771ed9862c4bf66329c","tid":314883,"uid":71154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>濕重 試下飲多d暖水<br />\n做運動出下汗<br />\n唔好飲同食凍野<br />\n調理下身體會好D<br />\n膊頭痛就比錢出去比人按下<br />\n按完包你一覺訓天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我已經痛到係街行一陣都開始痛<br />\n平時舉手都唔係點舉到<br />\n我懷疑緊自己係咪有五十肩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />